                "incident_source": [
                  "P-LI7"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The target system of the p-Li neutron field",
                "comprised of a 2 mm thick Li (7Li 99.98% enriched)",
                "target backing by a 12 mm thick carbon (graphite)",
                "used as a beam stopper for primary protons. The lithium",
                "target was fixed in an aluminum target holder, which",
                "enabled the target to slide up and down manually. This",
                "made it possible to irradiate samples using two types",
                "of target systems: one was a lithium-plus-carbon target",
                "the other was only carbon target.",
                "The neutron spectra at 0 degr. were measured with TOF",
                "method using a 127-mm-diam. x 127mm-long NE213",
                "scintillator about 10 m away from the target."
              ]
            }
